{"tid":1581205,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港民間議會籌備當中，依加要人！","createTime":"2019-09-19T12:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T15:22:35.000Z","uid":158270,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e7316599746dcb0b8520eb38d2b12dbaed5564","tid":1581205,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T12:33:04.000Z","msg":"Telegram公海：<a href=\"http://t.me/hkparliament\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkparliament&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IPxVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=485be208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkparliament</a><br />\n<br />\n現有機制已無法成代表民意。我相信只有自行成立民間議會，香港先會有出路。<br />\n<br />\n目前寫緊一個議會網站，以提議、辯論、表決方式表達民意。<br />\n惟目前缺乏知名度，大家見到嘅不妨入嚟睇下有咩做到。<br />\n現缺：議會憲章意見、文宣、法律知識、會計知識、任何熱心人士。<br />\n重要議題：法律責任、身份認證、收支平衡、議會定位（憲章）、議事規則<br />\n<br />\n暫定proposal: <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1zPOp9uMR0dBoaPvmBnGT_HGBsWXwAc_sWp3qIwo1fwM/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1zPOp9uMR0dBoaPvmBnGT_HGBsWXwAc_sWp3qIwo1fwM%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IPxVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=4557e5fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1zPOp9uMR0dBoaPvmBnGT_HGBsWXwAc_sWp3qIwo1fwM/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"4025191d7bfd8048df942208fb34be685bdef9f7","tid":1581205,"uid":187950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38e52fd3d85d906a161031a35d0a8329c03f63ac","tid":1581205,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T12:33:41.000Z","msg":"【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span styl